This product includes the following third-party open source components:

- PyMuPDF (AGPL-3.0) — PDF text extraction
- pdfplumber (MIT) — PDF table extraction
- pytesseract (Apache-2.0) — OCR wrapper for Tesseract
- python-docx (MIT) — DOCX parsing
- beautifulsoup4 (MIT) — HTML parsing
- html2text (GPL-3.0) — HTML to text conversion
- rapidfuzz (MIT) — Fuzzy string matching
- pydantic (MIT) — Data validation
- vsdx (MIT) — Visio file parsing
- Pillow (HPND) — Image processing
- pdf2image (MIT) — PDF to image conversion
- PyYAML (MIT) — YAML parsing

Tesseract OCR (Apache-2.0) and Pandoc (GPL-2.0) are optional system
dependencies and are not bundled with this software.
